{"prayers":[{"phelps":"BB00623","text":"## Blackfoot / Siksika\n\nApistotokeewa keeták-oXkotspómok-owa, kútat-sits-eéh’pa keeták-oXkot-spomókee? Ah-yoh Apistotokee! UnúX-kiy Apistotokee! Kunáy-tapee otés-pomok ki óXkunoX-pokee-woh-yah.\n\nIs there any Remover of difficulties save God? Say: Praised be God! He is God! All are His servants, and all abide by His bidding!.","name":"Blackfoot / Siksika","category":"Blackfoot / Siksika","order_in_cat":1,"source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"985ec695-00f3-4e0a-8a43-c18358d0c4c5","v":"90qt3ycus08c3aqju1pey529x","book_cats":{"af:bp":{"cat":"Toetse en Moeilikhede","order_in_cat":6},"ar:bp":{"cat":"الامتحانات والبلايا","order_in_cat":2},"az:bp":{"cat":"Sinaq və çətinliklərdə oxunan dualar","order_in_cat":5},"be:bp":{"cat":"Выпрабаванні і цяжкасці","order_in_cat":1},"bg:bp":{"cat":"Помощ в изпитания","order_in_cat":3},"bi:bp":{"cat":"TEKEMAOT  OL  TRABOL","order_in_cat":2},"bn:bp":{"cat":"পরীক্ষা ও  বিপদের সময়ের প্রার্থনা","order_in_cat":2},"bs:bp":{"cat":"Pomoć u Nevolji","order_in_cat":1},"ca:bp":{"cat":"Proves i Dificultats","order_in_cat":12},"ch:bp":{"cat":"OTRO SIHA NA TINAITAI","order_in_cat":6},"cnr:bp":{"cat":"Teškoće","order_in_cat":1},"co:bp":{"cat":"Assistenza","order_in_cat":1},"cs:bp":{"cat":"Pomoc a podpora","order_in_cat":2},"cy:bp":{"cat":"Assistance","order_in_cat":1},"da:bp":{"cat":"Prøvelser Og Vanskeligheder","order_in_cat":7},"de:bp":{"cat":"Prüfungen und Schwierigkeiten","order_in_cat":11},"dgz:bp":{"cat":"Koewa Toborapen U’uraewa (Assistance)","order_in_cat":1},"el:bp":{"cat":"∆ΟΚΙΜΑΣΙΩΝ ΚΑΙ ∆ΥΣΚΟΛΙΩΝ","order_in_cat":6},"en:bp":{"cat":"Tests and Difficulties","order_in_cat":5},"es:bp":{"cat":"Pruebas y Tribulaciones","order_in_cat":9},"eu:bp":{"cat":"Laguntza","order_in_cat":1},"fi:bp":{"cat":"Koettelemukset","order_in_cat":3},"fj:bp":{"cat":"NA VEIVUKEI KEI NA VEIVAKATOVOLEI","order_in_cat":1},"fo:bp":{"cat":"Royndir og Trupulleikar","order_in_cat":1},"fr:bp":{"cat":"Réconfort dans les épreuves","ord